text: Gnathoenia congoana is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Belon in 1901. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo.BioLib.cz - Gnathoenia congoana. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. It contains the varietas Gnathoenia congoana var. reticulata. ==References== Category:Ceroplesini Category:Beetles described in 1901
title: Gnathoenia congoana
